{"tha-ap305:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap305:0.2":"Padumakesaravagga ","tha-ap305:0.3":"Paramannadayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap305:1.1":"“Kanikaramva jotantam, ","tha-ap305:1.2":"udayantamva bhanumam; ","tha-ap305:1.3":"Vipassim addasam buddham, ","tha-ap305:1.4":"lokajettham narasabham. ","tha-ap305:2.1":"Anjalim paggahetvana, ","tha-ap305:2.2":"abhinesim sakam gharam; ","tha-ap305:2.3":"Abhinetvana sambuddham, ","tha-ap305:2.4":"paramannamadasaham. ","tha-ap305:3.1":"Ekanavutito kappe, ","tha-ap305:3.2":"paramannamadim tada; ","tha-ap305:3.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap305:3.4":"paramannassidam phalam. ","tha-ap305:4.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap305:4.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap305:4.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap305:5.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma paramannadayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap305:6.1":"Paramannadayakattherassapadanam tatiyam. "}